<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1896-09-08T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1896-09-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="682" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d682">
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Taylor</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">San
                                        Sebastian</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-09-08"><hi rend="italic">September 8,
                                    1896</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Minister of foreign affairs told me last night confidentially <hi rend="italic">Competitor</hi> case actually decided as indicated in
                            my last telegram. Will be made public soon. Cortes adjourned
                            yesterday.</p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>